               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-952" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-952" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-952" type="surname" value="LAMB"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-952" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD LAMB</persName>
                  </hi>. I lived at No. 9, Prince's-street, Turk-street, Bethnal-green, and am a shoemaker—the prisoner was in my service Five or Six weeks—he left me on the 25th of July; about six o'clock that day I missed the shoes and handkerchief, I went and took him into custody—the shoes have not been found—this handkerchief is mine.</p>
